    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 3 -1 50 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 8 0 0}I'm sorry I couldn't do more to help on my end.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
    <Page spk="0002"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 5 1 -1 50 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 9 0 0}I don't detect any more Shadows. Well done. You can come on back now.[n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
  </Dialog>
  <Dialog id="6" name="MSG_006_0_0" type="Message">
