    <Page spk="0000"><![CDATA[{f 0 5 254}{f 2 1}{f 4 5 3 3 -1 -1 0 0}{f 3 1 1 0 0 15 0 0}Anyone wanna grab a bite to eat on the way? I'm freakin' starving![n]{f 1 1}]]></Page>
